## Pagination

### ✅ Standard pagination pattern:
```python
@router.get("/", response_model=list[FeatureRead])
def list_features(
    skip: int = Query(default=0, ge=0, description="Items to skip"),
    limit: int = Query(default=20, ge=1, le=100, description="Max items")
) -> Sequence[Feature]:
    ...
```

### For large datasets, use cursor-based pagination:
```python
@router.get("/", response_model=PaginatedResponse[FeatureRead])
def list_features(
    cursor: Optional[str] = None,
    limit: int = Query(default=20, ge=1, le=100)
):
    # cursor is base64-encoded last ID
    ...
```

