## Request Validation

### ✅ Use Pydantic with Field constraints:
```python
from pydantic import Field

class FeatureCreate(SQLModel):
    title: str = Field(
        min_length=1, 
        max_length=255,
        description="Feature title"
    )
    description: Optional[str] = Field(
        default=None,
        max_length=5000,
        description="Optional description"
    )
    raw_requirements: str = Field(
        min_length=10,
        max_length=50000,
        description="Raw requirements text"
    )
```

